      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver verified against published benchmark cases for rotating-frame incompressible flow; MRL 2 requires Gradation 1.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent has been verified against the FDA Critical Path benchmark pump case (Hariharan et al. 2011) and the Taylor-Couette rotating-flow benchmark. Order-of-accuracy tests confirm second-order spatial convergence. Achieved level 2 exceeds the MRL 2 requirement of level 1."
    },
    {
